item.description:
Ahhaha&hellip;You got your fine tuned model trained in Jupyter notebook&hellip;now what&rsquo;s next?
Get it delivered to customers&hellip;ASAP. right? maybe&hellip;
There are some hurdles before deploying the model in Production which needs to be taken care of like data drift, model updation, and deploying model to edge devices comes with it own set of challenges. It isn&rsquo;t all software engineering, it&rsquo;s more than that and that&rsquo;s what we are going are cover in this specialization on MLOps — Machine Learning Operations.
